  <summary date="2025-08-13T18:29:41Z" status="Introduced in House">Debt Ceiling Reform Act

This bill replaces the existing federal debt limit with procedures that allow the Department of the Treasury to continue issuing additional debt unless a joint resolution of disapproval regarding the additional debt is enacted into law.&#160;The bill also requires Congress to consider the joint resolution using specified expedited legislative procedures.&#160;</summary>
